Following is a table of the world’s
10 biggest producers of refined nickel in 2011 by country,
compiled by Lisbon-based International Nickel Study Group.
Production figures are in thousands of metric tons. Chinese
figures include nickel pig iron output.  To contact the reporter on this story:
